<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="23May1930"><font color="red">23 May 1930</font> <i>BLHW</i> (to Harriet Weaver from Helen Fleischmann): &hellip; there is absolutely no news about his eye &hellip; he sees absolutely nothing with the eye. I arrived here last night from Paris &hellip; Lucia is home in my apartment </div>
